It=E2=80=99s been a marathon of week over here at Not Boring HQ. Big permit=
ting reform, AI doing a bunch of stuff better than humans, and Zuck droppin=
=E2=80=99 something. Speaking of marathons, Packy is running his first this=
 weekend in London. Good luck big bro!
Let=E2=80=99s get to it.
