/substack.com/redirect/dbd58ded-d8da-4a26-b04d-d41a2e90485e?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXA=
wZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ].
Stocks have been on a record run, which means portfolio diversification is =
more important now than ever.=20
Thousands of investors are turning to private credit as a potential hedge a=
gainst downturns and volatility. Private credit are loans negotiated privat=
ely and not by banks - that means they could have potentially higher yields=
 that are typically less correlated to public markets.
